+ Query Lifecycle\nUnity Catalog
++ Step 1: Submission
+++_ User / Service Principal
+++_ All-purpose / Job cluster\nor SQL warehouse
++ Step 2: Validation
+++_ UC checks permissions
+++_ Audit log recorded
+++_ Denied? Blocked + logged
++ Step 3: Cloud Credentials
+++_ Per object referenced
+++_ Managed tables → metastore
+++_ External tables → ext. location
++ Step 4: Scoped Tokens
+++_ Temp access token generated
+++_ Secure access URL provided
++ Step 5: Storage Access
+++_ Cluster uses token + URL
+++_ abfss:// ADLS Gen2

++ Step 6: Data Transfer
+++_ Storage returns data to compute
++ Step 7: Fine-grained Filtering
+++_ Row-level filtering
++++_ Per-user row visibility
+++_ Column masking
++++_ Sensitive fields redacted
++ Step 8: Result
+++_ Filtered result to caller
@endmindmap
